# Class-Based Testbench — Milestone 2 & 3

This directory contains all class-based verification components for the Multiprocessor System.

## How to Run

From Multiprocessor_System_MS2_Class/:

  vdel -lib work -all
  vlib work
  vlog -sv -mfcu -cover bcesf rtl/mp_dut.sv Class_TB/*.sv
  vsim -coverage work.tb_top
  run -all

## Component Descriptions

| File                  | Role                                                  |
|-----------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|
| transaction.sv        | Transaction object — opcode, addr, operands, data     |
| generator.sv          | Creates constrained random transactions               |
| driver.sv             | Translates transactions into DUT pin-level stimulus   |
| monitor_in.sv         | Observes and records inputs sent to DUT               |
| monitor_out.sv        | Captures DUT responses and forwards to scoreboard     |
| scoreboard.sv         | Reference model — predicts and checks results         |
| coverage_collector.sv | Tracks functional coverage across opcodes and cores   |
| environment.sv        | Instantiates and connects all components              |
| intf.sv               | SystemVerilog interface between TB and DUT            |
| tb_top.sv             | Top-level testbench module                            |
| run.do                | QuestaSim compile and simulate script                 |
